metadata.name: Ascension #023
metadata.description:
Svrite's genesis collection consists of 25 unique tokens, differentiated by color with each featuring the track 'I Hope You Listening', that grant owners access to an exclusive unreleased mixtape, Red Room Studio Tapes, additional exclusive content and access, and the initial buyers a FaceTime meet 'n greet with Svrite.  One lucky collector will receive a golden egg surprise of additional exclusive unreleased tracks and a Ledger Nano S hardware wallet. 
Featured Song: 'I Hope You Listening'
Performed by: Svrite
Written by: Svrite
Produced by:  Two Sides
